<section class="block" id="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Easy from start to finish</p>
      <h2>Your free measure &amp; quote in 4 simple steps</h2>
      <p>No showroom trips, no confusing catalogues. Just a friendly local who makes choosing blinds easy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">1</div>
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Book online or call</h3><p>Fill in the form or ring Jackson. Pick a time that suits — days, after work, or weekends.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">2</div>
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 13h13V6H3zM16 8h3l2 3v2h-5z"/><circle cx="7" cy="17" r="1.6"/><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="1.6"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Jackson comes to you</h3><p>He brings samples so you can see and feel the options against your own walls and light.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">3</div>
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8l13-5 5 13-13 5z"/><path d="M8 6l1 3M11 5l1 3M14 12l3-1M13 15l3-1"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Proper measure</h3><p>Every window measured accurately on the spot — the bit most people get wrong on their own.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="num">4</div>
        <div class="step-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M9 15l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Clear, fixed quote</h3><p>A tidy written price with no surprises. Happy to go ahead? We book your install.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
